p: The Kabutops has a strange metal device attached to its back.
\rThat Kabutops was the cause of all our problems.
\rIt escaped its enclosure and was trying to free the rest of them.
\rLemme just remove this machine from it...
\rThere! I think we can chalk that experiment up to a failure.
\rNevermind.\nWe can deal with the cleanup from here.
\g\rWe'll call you on your Pokegear if we need anything from you.
The scientists need help! I can't abandon them!
